quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,138,aur hum ne bani Israel ko darya ke paar utaara to woh aisay logon ke paas ja puhanche jo apne buton ( ki ibadat ) ke liye baithy rehtay they. ( bani Israel ) kehnay lagey ke moose jaisay un logon ke mabood hain. hamaray liye bhi aik mabood bana do. moose ne kaha ke tum barray hi jaahil log ho
  7,139,yeh log jis ( shugal ) mein ( phansay hue ) hain woh barbaad honay wala hai aur jo kaam yeh karte hain sab behooda hain
  7,140,( aur yeh bhi ) kaha ke bhala mein khuda ke siwa tumahray liye koi aur mabood talaash karoon halaank is ne tum ko tamam ahal aalam par fazeelat bakhsh hai
  7,141,( aur hamaray un ehsaanon ko yaad karo ) jab hum ne tum ko firounion ( ke haath ) se nijaat bakhsh woh log tum ko bara dukh dete they. tumahray beton ko qatal kar daaltay they aur baityon ko zindah rehne dete they. aur is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se sakht azmaish thi
  7,142,aur hum ne moose se tees raat ki meyaad muqarrar ki. aur is das ( raatain ) aur mila kar usay poora ( chilla ) kardiya to is ke perwar-digaar ki chalees raat ki meyaad poori hogayi. aur moose ne apne bhai Haroon se kaha ke mere ( Koh tor par jaane ke ) baad tum meri qoum mein mere janasheen ho ( un ki ) islaah karte rehna theek aur shariron ke raste nah chalna
  7,143,aur jab moose hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par ( koh tor ) par puhanche aur un ke perwar-digaar ne un se kalaamkiya to kehnay lagey ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( jalva ) dikha ke mein tera deedar ( bhi ) daikhon. perwar-digaar ne kaha ke tum mujhe hargiz nah dekh sakuu ge. haan pahar ki taraf dekhte raho agar yeh apni jagah qaim raha to tum mujhe dekh sakuu ge. jab un ka perwar-digaar pahar par namodaar howa to ( tajallii anwaar Rabbani ) ne is ko rezah rezah kardiya aur moose be hosh ho kar gir parre. jab hosh mein aeye to kehnay lagey ke teri zaat pak hai aur mein tairay huzoor tauba karta hon aur jo imaan laane walay hain un mein sab se awwal hon
